Ex-BBNaija’s housemate Erica has admonished fans sending gifts to her through her mom to stop. The 27-year-old reality TV star stated this via her Twitter handle. According to her, these gifts sent through the mother are obviously from her “frenenemy”, using such opportunity to get information and she doesn’t appreciate it.   Mum’s desperation for male child blessed me – Williams…     Age, grade don’t determine maturity – Regina Daniels     Reality finer than filter – Mercy Johnson   Expressing displeasure, she noted that these gifts are from Kiddricca fans- these are supporters of Kiddwaya and Erica’s relationship during the show. She tweets: “I think it’s very weird that some fans have decided to start talking to my mother and using gifts as an excuse to get information. “Gifts used to be sent to my Pa, all of a sudden my mum is the one you want to send to why??? And it’s not Elites it’s the frenemy fan base. Stop it! “Kiddrica fan base to be precise, stop it! I don’t appreciate it in anyway.”